<item>
            <title>[SYNAPSE-977] Issue with Header mediator with complex headers</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-977</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In the following configuration, if the message goes through the case path, complex header value is changed using the enrich mediator.&lt;br/&gt;
At the same time header mediator value is also getting changed.&lt;br/&gt;
So after one request goes through the case path, any other subsequent messages will also get the header value set by the enrich mediator even they are not dispatched through the case path.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;definitions xmlns=&quot;http://ws.apache.org/ns/synapse&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;proxy name=&quot;HeaderAndEnrichTest&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
          transports=&quot;https http&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
          startOnLoad=&quot;true&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
          trace=&quot;disable&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;description/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;target&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;inSequence&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;property name=&quot;HEADER_PROP&quot; value=&quot;foo&quot; scope=&quot;default&quot; type=&quot;STRING&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;header scope=&quot;default&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
               &amp;lt;m:complexHeader xmlns:m=&quot;http://org.synapse.example&quot;&amp;gt;TEST&amp;lt;/m:complexHeader&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;/header&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;switch xmlns:ns=&quot;http://org.apache.synapse/xsd&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
                    xmlns:m0=&quot;http://services.samples&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
                    source=&quot;//m0:symbol&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
               &amp;lt;case regex=&quot;MSFT&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                  &amp;lt;enrich&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                     &amp;lt;source type=&quot;property&quot; clone=&quot;true&quot; property=&quot;HEADER_PROP&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                     &amp;lt;target xmlns:m=&quot;http://org.synapse.example&quot; xpath=&quot;$header/m:complexHeader&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                  &amp;lt;/enrich&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
               &amp;lt;/case&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
               &amp;lt;default/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;/switch&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;send&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
               &amp;lt;endpoint&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                  &amp;lt;address uri=&quot;http://localhost:9000/services/SimpleStockQuoteService&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
               &amp;lt;/endpoint&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;/send&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;/inSequence&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;/target&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;/proxy&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/definitions&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
